N2  - The application of a computerized optimum-seeking search procedure, called Razor Search, to large-scale simulation experiments is presented using the language of control theory. Results of the search procedure's use with the Urban Dynamics model are given and discussed.
AB  - The application of a computerized optimum-seeking search procedure, called Razor Search, to large-scale simulation experiments is presented using the language of control theory. Results of the search procedure's use with the Urban Dynamics model are given and discussed.
